                  "revisionId": 2793485,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "Link Redirection will allow most direct forms of shield recovery to apply to the pet, including Harrow 's Condemn , Hildryn 's Pillage , the Rakta Dark Dagger 's passive, Volt 's Capacitance , and Protea 's Grenade Fan ."
